title: The Awakening of Europe
creator: M. B. Synge
description: LibriVox recording of The Awakening of Europe, by M. B. Synge. Read by Laura Caldwell. The Awakening of Europe by M. B. Synge is the third book in the series, Story of the World. Included in this history is a myriad of interesting men, women, and events that shaped Europe during the years 1520-1745. (Summary by Laura Caldwell) M4B audiobook of complete book For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
